    "answer_id" : 46841757,
    "question_id" : 2330942,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Yes Java allows <code>vargs</code> in method parameter . </p>\n\n<pre><code>public class  Varargs\n{\n   public int add(int... numbers)\n   { \n      int result = 1; \n      for(int number: numbers)\n      {\n         result= result+number;  \n      }  return result; \n   }\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
